    graph = [[] for i in range(n+1)]
    for i in range(m):
        u, v = map(int, input().split())
        graph[u].append(v)
        graph[v].append(u)
    visited = [False] * (n+1)
    visited[1] = True
    queue = [1]
    time = 0
    while queue:
        for i in range(len(queue)):
            node = queue.pop(0)
            for j in graph[node]:
                if not visited[j]:
                    visited[j] = True
                    queue.append(j)
        time += 1
    print(time)

    a = list(map(int, input().split()))
    count = 0
    for i in range(1, n):
        if a[i] < a[i-1]:
            count += 1
            a[i] = (a[i] + m) % m
    print(count)
